OL,3,CLabour highlight 'Martyn's Law' by
OL,4,Ccommitting to anti-terrorism
OL,5,Clegislation
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has committed to
OL,8,Fintroducing 'Martyn's Law' under a
OL,9,FLabour government, after a new anti-
OL,10,Fterrorism bill featured in the King's
OL,11,FSpeech.
OL,13,FDuring the speech, King Charles said
OL,14,Flegislation would be introduced to
OL,15,Fimprove safety and security of public
OL,16,Fvenues to 'keep the British public
OL,17,Fsafe from terrorism'.
