OL,3,CLabour highlight 'Martyn's Law' by
OL,4,Ccommitting to anti-terrorism
OL,5,Clegislation
OL,7,FThe 'Terrorism (Protection of
OL,8,FPremises) Bill' will enact 'Martyn's
OL,9,FLaw', requiring large venues to put in
OL,10,Fplace anti-terrorism measures to
OL,11,Ftackle terror threats.
OL,13,FWhat is Martyn's Law?
OL,15,FMartyn's Law is named after 29-year-
OL,16,Fold Martyn Hett, who was one of the 22
OL,17,Fpeople killed in the 2017 Manchester
OL,18,FArena attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
