OL,5,Clegislation
OL,7,FPremises with a capacity of between
OL,8,F100 and 799 will be considered
OL,9,F'standard tier', and those with a
OL,10,Fhigher capacity of 800 will be classed
OL,11,Fas an 'enhanced tier'.
OL,13,FWithin 'standard tier', venues will
OL,14,Fneed to undertake low-cost effective
OL,15,Fmeasures such as training, information
OL,16,Fsharing, and completion of a
OL,17,Fpreparedness plan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
