OL,7,FMeanwhile, 'enhanced tier' venues will
OL,8,Fbe required to undertake an additional
OL,9,Frisk assessment that will inform the
OL,10,Fdevelopment and implementation of a
OL,11,Fthorough security plan.
OL,13,FFigen Murray has been campaigning for
OL,14,Fchange since 2019, after an online
OL,15,Fpetition calling on increased security
OL,16,Fchecks in public venues, reached over
OL,17,F23,000 signatures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
