OL,7,FSince then she has been working with
OL,8,Fcampaigners, meeting with government
OL,9,Fofficials regularly to formulate how
OL,10,Fthe law could be implemented.
OL,12,FShe was awarded an OBE in the 2022 New
OL,13,FYear's Honours List for her work in
OL,14,Fcounter-terrorism.
OL,16,FIn May 2022, Martyn's Law was
OL,17,Fconfirmed to proceed in Queen's
OL,18,FSpeech, setting out the then
OL,19,Fgovernment's planned legislative
OL,20,Fprogramme.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
