OL,5,Clegislation
OL,7,FMs Murray then spoke with the then
OL,8,FPrime Minister over the phone in
OL,9,FDecember 2022, where Rishi Sunak said
OL,10,Fhe was committed to improving security
OL,11,Fmeasures.
OL,13,FHowever, the impact of the Covid-19
OL,14,Fpandemic and a number of leadership
OL,15,Fchanges in government, led to various
OL,16,Fdelays in bringing legislation forward.
OL,18,FAs a result, Ms Murray took the
OL,19,Fdecision to walk 200 miles from
OL,20,FManchester Arena to 10 Downing Street
OL,21,Fto meet with Mr Sunak in May this year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
