OL,7,FResponding to the comments by the
OL,8,Fbereaved mother, the PM insisted
OL,9,F"there's no change to the timeline" he
OL,10,Fpromised Ms Murray.
OL,12,FMr Sunak said he's still "working
OL,13,Ftowards bringing forward Martyn's
OL,14,FLaw... We've got an election, and the
OL,15,Felection's in the beginning of July
OL,16,Fand my plan is very much to bring that
OL,17,Flaw forward."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
