OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer also met with Ms
OL,8,FMurray during her visit to London,
OL,9,Ftelling the House of Commons "we must
OL,10,Fmake (Martyn's Law) a reality as soon
OL,11,Fas possible."
OL,13,FLaying out the government's priorities
OL,14,Funder Labour in parliament on 17 June,
OL,15,FKing Charles highlighted the
OL,16,Fimportance of 'keeping the British
OL,17,Fpublic safe from terrorism'.
